text.tspan: The Dashboard is the central hub of AkuntansiKu, designed to give users a clear and
instant view of the company’s financial position. It summarizes key financial activities,
ensuring that decision-makers can monitor performance in real time with ease and
Visualizes the flow of financial transactions across different accounts and categories.
Users can instantly see where funds move, identify trends, and monitor cash flow
Equity – owner’s capital and retained earnings
Revenue & Expenses – income streams and operational costs
Provides clarity for account-level analysis and financial transparency.
